bitamin_a = cbind(bitamin, grade = ifelse(bitamin$test < 65,'F',ifelse(bitamin$test >= 65 & bitamin$test <75, 'C', ifelse(75<=bitamin$test & bitamin$test < 85, 'B', ifelse(85<= bitamin$test,'A','other')))))
